  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 3 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  delayBetweenCharacters: 0.1
  delayBetweenLines: 2
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - 'Just this morning, we have confirmed a third symptom that may appear as a result
    of the virus. '
  - Infected individuals experience discolouration of the chest alongside previously
    mentioned symptoms.
  - However, if the discolouration of the chest is seen at the same time as a rash
    on the arm, then neither of these symptoms are to be considered when determining
    if an individual is infected.
  - Any citizens who experience any symptoms that suggest that may be infected must
    contact us via their computer messaging application immediately.
